author: COMSOL
description: This benchmark reproduces the two test cases from the ISO 10077-2:2012 standard related to roller shutters. The thermal performance of each shutter is computed from its thermal conductance and thermal transmittance. Finally, the results are compared with given data for validation.
label: roller_shutter_thermal_performances.mph
